.TH VV-CONTEXT-DIFF 1 "2026-03-11" "vv 0.8.0-6-gffbff18" "Vibe-Vault Manual"
.SH NAME
vv-context-diff \- show diffs for outdated project commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vv context diff [\-\-project <name>]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Shows unified diffs for project commands that have pending template updates.
.PP
When "vv context sync" detects that a vault template has changed since the
project command was created, it writes a .pending sidecar and reports OUTDATED.
This command shows what changed so you can decide whether to accept the update
or keep your version.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-project <name>
Override auto\-detected project name
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
vv context diff                       Diff current project
vv context diff \-\-project myproject   Diff a specific project
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vv (1),
.BR vv\-context (1),
.BR vv\-context\-sync (1),
.BR vv\-context\-accept (1)
